# ⚡ 7. Availability vs Reliability

| Feature | Availability       | Reliability            |
| ------- | ------------------ | ---------------------- |
| Meaning | System is up       | System works correctly |
| Focus   | Uptime             | Correctness            |
| Example | Website accessible | Correct data returned  |


#⚡ 8.   Scalability vs Availability

| Feature      | Scalability 🚀           | Availability 🔄 |
| ------------ | ------------------------ | --------------- |
| Focus        | Handle more load         | Stay online     |
| Goal         | Performance under growth | No downtime     |
| Example      | Add servers              | Backup servers  |
| Failure case | Slow system              | System down     |
